    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "Well-kept car in good overall condition that shows nicely and should make a solid driver. The exterior and interior present well with the kind of normal light wear you\u2019d expect from a used vehicle, but nothing suggesting neglect or major cosmetic issues. Overall, it feels cared for, with good fit and finish and plenty of life left for the next owner.",
      "price": 33900.0,
