    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "Well-kept, honest driver in good overall condition. It presents nicely inside and out, with the kind of normal cosmetic wear, small blemishes, and age-related imperfections you\u2019d expect from a used car that has been driven and maintained rather than hidden away. The interior is clean and usable, the exterior shows well overall, and it should make a solid choice for someone looking for a car they can enjoy right away while still expecting the occasional minor item that comes with age.",
      "price": 33900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 14
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Affordable project car with real potential for the right buyer. This one is in poor condition and will need repairs, cleanup, and mechanical attention before it\u2019s ready for dependable regular use, but it could be a worthwhile option for someone handy or looking for a budget build. If you want a cheap starting point and understand it needs work, this could be a great fit.",
      "price": 4200.0,
