      "timestep_posted": 14
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Priced to move, this vehicle offers a practical, budget-friendly way to get behind the wheel without a major investment. It shows its age and is best suited for a buyer who values affordability and straightforward transportation, with plenty of potential for someone handy or looking for an inexpensive project. A sensible opportunity to own a vehicle at a very accessible price point.",
      "price": 4950.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 14
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels with plenty of life left for the right buyer? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it starts, runs, and offers a great opportunity for someone who wants dependable basic transportation, a project, or a handy second vehicle. I\u2019m being upfront that it shows its age and needs some TLC, but that\u2019s exactly why it\u2019s priced to make sense. If you want something honest, budget-friendly, and worth a look, this could be a great fit.",
      "price": 6900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 14
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid budget-friendly driver/project with good bones. Starts, runs, and moves under its own power, with an engine that pulls cleanly and a drivetrain that feels usable for daily puttering or weekend wrenching. Suspension, braking, and steering are all presentable enough to make this a practical base for someone who wants an inexpensive car to sort, improve, or simply use as-is. Cosmetically it shows age and wear, but that is reflected in the price. If you know how to turn a wrench, this is the kind of entry-point car that can be enjoyed immediately while you tackle the details over time.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 14
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Runs. Drives. Cheap way into a car now. Not pretty, but it gets the job done. Priced to move fast.",
      "price": 7900.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 14
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Here\u2019s a car with stories in its bones and plenty of road left for someone who sees potential. It\u2019s not pretending to be showroom fresh\u2014this is the kind of ride for a practical buyer, weekend tinkerer, or anyone looking for an affordable set of wheels with real character. The body and cabin show their age, but that lived-in feel gives it an honest, no-nonsense presence. Whether you need a budget-friendly commuter, a backup vehicle, or a project to make your own, this one offers a chance to get behind the wheel without breaking the bank.",
      "price": 6900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 14
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and priced to move, this vehicle offers an affordable way into dependable basic transportation. It shows its age and is best suited for a value-focused buyer who wants a practical car at an accessible price point. A straightforward opportunity for someone comfortable with a well-used vehicle and looking for strong bang for the buck.",
      "price": 4950.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 14
    }
